      "text": "# Schema\n\n### Loopbacks\n- **Loopback0**\n  - Fabric A: 10.254.1.**<NodeID>/32**\n  - Fabric B: 10.254.2.**<NodeID>/32**\n- **Loopback1**\n  - Fabric A: 10.255.1.**<NodeID>/32**\n  - Fabric B: 10.255.2.**<NodeID>/32**\n\n### MLAG\n- Domain ID: **100**\n- Peer-Link: **Port-Channel1000**\n- Peer Sync Interface: **Vlan4094**\n- Peer Sync Prefix: **169.254.0.0/30**\n- Peer OSPF Peering Interface: **Vlan4093**\n- Peer OSPF Peering Prefix: **192.0.0.0/30**\n\n### Inter-Fabric IP Transport\n  - Point-to-Point IP Block: **172.16.255.0/24**\n  - Routing Protocol: **OSPF (Area 0)**\n\n",
